         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility"> ¶ 24/11/88 ¶  ¶ Yesterday evening, my dear Krichauff, I received your kind letter. ¶ Letter not found. ¶  ¶ Please accept my best thanks for your felicitation on the brilliant event in my scientific ...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="de">88.11.24a</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="de">To Friedrich Krichauff</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="de">Private hands</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="de">24/11/88</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Gestern Abend, mein lieber Krichauff, erhielt ich Deinen gütigen Brief. Nimm meinen besten Dank hin für Deine Felicitation zu dem glänzenden Ereigniss in meinem Wissenschafts Leben! Ich bin besonders stolz darauf, dass einem<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">Deutschen</hi>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>diese so selten Auszeichnung<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>zuerst<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>in Australien zuerkoren wurde. Ich muss versuchen Dich persönlich aufzufinden während Deines kurzen Hierseins.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ich habe mich kaum von meinem Unfall erholt, so dass ich überhaupt erst 2 mal in der Centennial Ausstellung gewesen bin.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ich hoffte, Du würdest uns mit den Deinen noch einen längeren Besuch während der Ausstellungs Zeit zu wenden. Hoffentlich hast Du Dich ganz erholt.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">Freundshaftlich</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>stets der Deine</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>24/11/88</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Yesterday evening, my dear Krichauff, I received your kind letter.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Letter not found.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>Please accept my best thanks for your felicitation on the brilliant event in my scientific life!<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn1" n="2">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>M had been awarded by the Royal Society of London one of its two Royal Medals for 1888.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>I am particularly proud that<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>this so rare honour was<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>awarded<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>first to<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>a German<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>in Australia. I must try to find you<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>in person<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>during your short stay here.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I have barely recovered from my accident,<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn2" n="3">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>M had fallen off a tram on 31 July and was seriously injured (<seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">Argus</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">
                           <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        </seg>(Melbourne), 1 August 1888, p. 7).</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>so I have only been to the Centennial Exhibition twice.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I hoped<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>that you and yours<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>would<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>pay us a longer visit during the exhibition period. I hope you have recovered completely.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn3" n="4">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="background-color: #FFFF00; ">Explain?</seg>
                     </p>
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="color: #2B4AFF; ">Krichauff</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="color: #2B4AFF; ">
                           <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>had arrived in Melbourne</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="color: #2B4AFF; ">
                           <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>on 2</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="color: #2B4AFF; ">3</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="color: #2B4AFF; ">
                           <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>November</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="color: #2B4AFF; ">.</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="color: #2B4AFF; ">
                           <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        </seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="color: #2B4AFF; ">He</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="color: #2B4AFF; ">
                           <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>and other members of the SA parliament were</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="color: #2B4AFF; ">
                           <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>listed as 'boudoir car passenger</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="color: #2B4AFF; ">s</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="color: #2B4AFF; ">' for Melbourne on the November 22 train</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="color: #2B4AFF; ">, returning on the 26 November</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="color: #2B4AFF; ">
                           <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        </seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="color: #2B4AFF; ">(</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont"
                             style="font-style: italic; color: #2B4AFF; ">South Australian register</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="color: #2B4AFF; ">, 23 November 1888, p. 5 and<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        </seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont"
                             style="font-style: italic; color: #2B4AFF; ">South Australian register</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="color: #2B4AFF; ">
                           <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>27 November 1888, p. 6).</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="color: #2B4AFF; ">
                           <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>No reference to Krichauff being ill at this time has been found.</seg>
                     </p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="margin-left: 1.75in; font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Amicably</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="margin-left: 1.75in; font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>always yours</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="margin-left: 1.75in; font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller</p>
         </div>
